          <div class="tech-chip chip-sf"><span class="chip-icon">📦</span>SCM 최적화</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-sf"><span class="chip-icon">📐</span>PLM</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-data"><span class="chip-icon">📊</span>BI 대시보드</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-data"><span class="chip-icon">🧠</span>수요 예측 AI</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-data"><span class="chip-icon">🌐</span>전사 Digital Twin</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-human"><span class="chip-icon">👥</span>경영 의사결정 지원</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- L3 MES -->
      <div class="layer-row">
        <div class="layer-label">
          <div class="ll-level">LEVEL 3</div>
          <div class="ll-name">제조 운영</div>
          <div class="ll-time">⏱ 분~시간</div>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-techs">
          <div class="tech-chip chip-sf chip-core"><span class="chip-icon">🏭</span>MES / MOM</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-sf"><span class="chip-icon">✅</span>QMS (품질관리)</div>
