          <div class="tech-chip chip-data"><span class="chip-icon">🧠</span>공정 최적화 AI</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-data"><span class="chip-icon">📈</span>SPC 통계분석</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-human"><span class="chip-icon">📱</span>작업 지시 / AR 가이드</div>
