        </div>
        <div class="layer-techs">
          <div class="tech-chip chip-sf chip-core" style="box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(16,185,129,0.15);"><span class="chip-icon">⚡</span>PLC / PAC</div>
          <div class="tech-chip chip-robot chip-core"><span class="chip-icon">🦾</span>6축 로봇 컨트롤러</div>
